h4. Actor:
Director, Project Director.

h4. Description:
This is landing page of *Purchase Order* with input form on top and grid view at the bottom.

h4. Flow:
* Actor Clicks [Procurement|guide:_widgetofprocurement] option from top menu bar.
* "Procurement" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click *Purchase Order* link.
* Show Landing Page of *Purchase Order*.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Show Purchase Order" privilege.

h4. Process:
* [Get List of all "Purchase Order" from server|guide:ListPurchaseOrderActionService].

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show input form on top to [Create "Purchase Order"|guide:CreatePurchaseOrderActionService].
** Show list of all *Purchase Order* in grid view of landing page.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].

h4. Related Usecase:
